{"tid":1421771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔洗咁激動屌黑警播片，預左佢地會用呢招","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:29:45.000Z","uid":47905,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"756281cb2d6b8109d79a53fa317026428c32bca7","tid":1421771,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得好多人搞錯左民間記者會既用意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420600</a><br />\n<br />\n我地都諗到 佢點會諗唔到<br />\n佢地播仲好，我哋可以正面抽擊<br />\n<br />\n搵返佢播既片 cut 左既部分 還原真相<br />\n搵返佢地既聲明 正面抽擊<br />\n搵使用象膠彈 布袋彈既使用指引 證明佢地使用過大武力，隔離Post 有講幾時可以用，係要對等武力<br />\n<br />\n我哋所有既野，唔需要幾個記者會就播晒<br />\n每個記者會播幾段<br />\n最好搵埋當事人受害者上去講解<br />\n無就cut 返 當時受訪片段<br />\n<br />\n明白大家好激氣，但沉著應戰"},{"pid":"81c48cff9d6ad7069aef7cbe29f0024a7256ff09","tid":1421771,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a92adcb26a74c0d223167fdc34d9c45c901b9d","tid":1421771,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n但要有人真係幫佢哋整理啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949df5437ac13fc7cbdf556005e5ad274179867b","tid":1421771,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db1fc960360b144e79f6e183bcc1ee4c847611b","tid":1421771,"uid":92347,